{"tid":2056875,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蔣旻正：譴責教協誤導公眾","createTime":"2020-06-09T04:10:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-09T05:09:59.000Z","uid":303498,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"69294cfb5a2a7d1922a5ab3a107a7cbbe9f3c30b","tid":2056875,"uid":303498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T04:10:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=271942564157043&amp;id=101953674489267\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D271942564157043%26id%3D101953674489267&d=N73AYdKZ8ITSJgwUZ5%2B19nG%2F0kAjhv1dd93UXbk31gU%3D&h=35467975\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=271942564157043&amp;id=101953674489267</a><br />\n<br />\n【譴責教協誤導公眾】<br />\n.<br />\n在今天《立場》 @thestandnews 報導中，教協會長馮偉華表示：早前與蔣旻正會面時，對方一直未能交代如何舉行初選，只表示可由戴耀廷處理。但馮偉華指，戴耀廷一直沒有聯絡他們。<br />\n.<br />\n本人認為此說明顯誤導公眾，陷戴耀廷與本人於不義，本人認為必須澄清。馮在言辭中，暗示本人不負責任，只把責任推卸於戴教授。並明言，戴教授沒有一直沒有聯絡他們。<br />\n.<br />\n事實上，是他們主動聯絡戴教授表明不會參加初選，卻以語言偽術包裝成戴教授不聯絡他們。<br />\n.<br />\n本人一介補習老師，反修例前從沒有想過參與政治，參與區議會時曾經讓區給同路人，以己身堵塞其他白區。當選後以區議員身分為還柙手足送補習筆者，已心滿意足，承蒙教育界同行不嫌棄，支持我參與教育界初選。自問協調過程中已盡全力，我一介素人，不懂政治手腕，知無不言，言無不盡，一切只求無愧於心，心安理得。<br />\n.<br />\n已知會戴教授公開對話以證彼此清白，讓公眾知情，作出公論。如為戴教授造成任何不便，實在非常抱歉。<br />\n.<br />\n蔣旻正<br />\n2020年6月8日 11:25pm<br />\n.<br />\n#教協 #為人師表<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FsUtxxF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFsUtxxF.jpg&h=40cf7b73&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HbasN51.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHbasN51.jpg&h=3074c7f2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/06/09/121001_dc8745da563c0de7b0e72e2795d17141.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F06%2F09%2F121001_dc8745da563c0de7b0e72e2795d17141.jpeg&h=af7daca0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/06/09/121003_ad0e0b9f9ac08bf44968c67d9f8f0ce2.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F06%2F09%2F121003_ad0e0b9f9ac08bf44968c67d9f8f0ce2.jpeg&h=d4131b8e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9d1d0e5e388130bf8af2b593427892acf7a7a31b","tid":2056875,"uid":303498,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T04:13:19.000Z","msg":"簡單而言，教協唔肯參加初選，仲要賴素人，老屎忽霸住個位"},{"pid":"43adbd3deacbe2663adfd2090a2c7590f555b299","tid":2056875,"uid":277702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T04:24:43.000Z","msg":"教育界啲人係咁上下⋯⋯"},{"pid":"668bf1a0d6c10f4495f6514c31396fb6784ce2f0","tid":2056875,"uid":300542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T05:09:59.000Z","msg":"真係恰尻你素人不懂政治手腕"}]}